Message.SourceString: Got a tail coming up fast…
Message.LocalizedString: Got a tail coming up fast…

Message.SourceString:
Doesn’t look that fast…
might as well have some fun…
Message.LocalizedString:
Doesn’t look that fast…
might as well have some fun…

Message.SourceString: …Heh, I thought we were keeping a low profile?
Message.LocalizedString: …Heh, I thought we were keeping a low profile?

Message.SourceString: Once in a while… why not?
Message.LocalizedString: Once in a while… why not?

Message.SourceString:
Drifting’s as easy as breakfast…
it’s my specialty.
Message.LocalizedString:
Drifting’s as easy as breakfast…
it’s my specialty.

Message.SourceString:
Stop it! Keisuke of Project D
wouldn’t say that!
Message.LocalizedString:
Stop it! Keisuke of Project D
wouldn’t say that!

Message.SourceString:
Alright then… here comes
Keisuke’s technique…!
Message.LocalizedString:
Alright then… here comes
Keisuke’s technique…!

Message.SourceString:
With due respect… Fujiwara here…
my game is flawless control.
Message.LocalizedString:
With due respect… Fujiwara here…
my game is flawless control.

Message.SourceString:
An inside pass on me…
that’s not a thing‼
Message.LocalizedString:
An inside pass on me…
that’s not a thing‼

Message.SourceString:
You’re the type to face
Purple Shadow next, right?
Message.LocalizedString:
You’re the type to face
Purple Shadow next, right?

Message.SourceString: Honestly, those guys are no joke.
Message.LocalizedString: Honestly, those guys are no joke.

Message.SourceString: Even Fujiwara and Keisuke only barely won…
Message.LocalizedString: Even Fujiwara and Keisuke only barely won…

Message.SourceString:
Old friends’ privilege…
I’ll brief you on the course.
Message.LocalizedString:
Old friends’ privilege…
I’ll brief you on the course.

Message.SourceString:
This course has lots of
long, sweeping corners.
Message.LocalizedString:
This course has lots of
long, sweeping corners.

Message.SourceString: Blind exits mean no letup… hard to send it.
Message.LocalizedString: Blind exits mean no letup… hard to send it.

Message.SourceString: (…All borrowed from Fujiwara and Keisuke, though.)
Message.LocalizedString: (…All borrowed from Fujiwara and Keisuke, though.)

Message.SourceString: Yo, hold up! I’m helping here!
Message.LocalizedString: Yo, hold up! I’m helping here!

Message.SourceString:
Rule is… whoever wins 
takes on the mountain god.
Message.LocalizedString:
Rule is… whoever wins 
takes on the mountain god.

Message.SourceString:
As a warm-up,
there’s no better battle than this…!
Message.LocalizedString:
As a warm-up,
there’s no better battle than this…!

Message.SourceString:
…Heh, Daiki gets passed
this easily, huh…
Message.LocalizedString:
…Heh, Daiki gets passed
this easily, huh…

Message.SourceString: Now I just hold the lead and win!
Message.LocalizedString: Now I just hold the lead and win!

Message.SourceString:
Purple Shadow and Todo School
have been rivals for years…
Message.LocalizedString:
Purple Shadow and Todo School
have been rivals for years…

Message.SourceString: Whoever you are, I’m not giving this up…!
Message.LocalizedString: Whoever you are, I’m not giving this up…!

Message.SourceString: How do you stay on throttle there…!?
Message.LocalizedString: How do you stay on throttle there…!?

Message.SourceString: How much stronger can you get, you bastard!!
Message.LocalizedString: How much stronger can you get, you bastard!!

Message.SourceString: I’ll give you my full effort.
Message.LocalizedString: I’ll give you my full effort.

Message.SourceString: No wonder Ryosuke vouches for you.
Message.LocalizedString: No wonder Ryosuke vouches for you.

Message.SourceString: There’s still excess in your inputs.
Message.LocalizedString: There’s still excess in your inputs.

Message.SourceString:
Don’t be disappointed…
it’s not that you’re bad.
Message.LocalizedString:
Don’t be disappointed…
it’s not that you’re bad.

Message.SourceString: There’s no doubt you have outstanding talent…
Message.LocalizedString: There’s no doubt you have outstanding talent…

Message.SourceString: If you can turn this experience into fuel to grow, that’s good…
Message.LocalizedString: If you can turn this experience into fuel to grow, that’s good…

Message.SourceString: Now then… I’ll run away… no need to save tires…
Message.LocalizedString: Now then… I’ll run away… no need to save tires…

Message.SourceString:
I’ll burn the remaining grip and
disappear from your sight‼
Message.LocalizedString:
I’ll burn the remaining grip and
disappear from your sight‼

Message.SourceString:
How… you shouldn’t have
enough tire left for this…
Message.LocalizedString:
How… you shouldn’t have
enough tire left for this…

Message.SourceString: I don’t spend time reading folks.
Message.LocalizedString: I don’t spend time reading folks.

Message.SourceString: All gas from the start… quick finish‼
Message.LocalizedString: All gas from the start… quick finish‼

Message.SourceString:
Opening the gap‼
Foot down, mouth on‼
Message.LocalizedString:
Opening the gap‼
Foot down, mouth on‼

Message.SourceString: Good… I see why Jo gets hyped‼
Message.LocalizedString: Good… I see why Jo gets hyped‼

Message.SourceString:
…Don’t downplay
how I mesh with this R34‼
Message.LocalizedString:
…Don’t downplay
how I mesh with this R34‼

Message.SourceString:
Heh… impressive…‼
Had me stunned for a sec…!
Message.LocalizedString:
Heh… impressive…‼
Had me stunned for a sec…!

Message.SourceString:
We’re past reason here…
no one gets to judge…‼
Message.LocalizedString:
We’re past reason here…
no one gets to judge…‼

Message.SourceString: Damn it… half a tire’s width understeer, huh⁉
Message.LocalizedString: Damn it… half a tire’s width understeer, huh⁉
